Package: android-platform-libcore-6.0.1-source
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: lang, utils, network, IO of Android Frameworks - Source code
 This package provides the Java source code of portions of the Android Framework
 of API Level 23 (Marshmallow).
 .
 The Android Framework "android.jar" should be built into one single artifact.
 However AOSP has separated the source code into two places, that's why this
 package is released as source code.
